        SparkeyReader duplicate()

      • iterator

        Iterator<SparkeyReader.Entry> iterator()
        Get an iterator over all the live entries. The iterator object is not thread safe, and the entry objects are highly volatile and will be invalidated by the next iteration step. Don't leak this entry, copy whatever data you want from it instead.
        Specified by:
        iterator in interface Iterable<SparkeyReader.Entry>
        Returns:
        an iterator
